      <li><span class="font-semibold">Customizable Solutions</span>: Trays and totes tailored to specific crops, harvest volumes, and operational needs.</li>
      <li><span class="font-semibold">Automation Compatibility</span>: Trays and totes designed for automated packing and sorting systems.</li>
      <li><span class="font-semibold">Consumer-Centric Design</span>: Packaging that enhances retail appeal while protecting produce.</li>
